Interface IPetriNet

All Known Implementing Classes:
PetriNet
public interface IPetriNet
Interface IPetriNet defines the core methods for managing and executing a PetriNet model. Provides methods for adding and removing places, transitions, and arcs, as well as running the PetriNet.
